					</footer><!-- .entry-meta --></article><!-- #post-72369 --><article id="post-72394" class="post-72394 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-staff category-schools"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://jordandistrict.org/2020/04/a-message-to-students-from-governor-herbert/" rel="bookmark">A Message to Students from Governor Herbert</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date" datetime="2020-04-28T16:53:17-06:00">April 28, 2020</time>
</div>
<!-- .entry-meta -->
			
					</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
			<p>We were asked to share this video message from Governor Herbert with all Jordan School District students.</p>
<p><iframe title="Governor Gary R  Herbert’s message to Utah students" width="584" height="329" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SJKYwbkXJns?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
