					</footer><!-- .entry-meta --></article><!-- #post-72389 --><article id="post-72383" class="post-72383 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-schools"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://jordandistrict.org/2020/04/additional-lunch-sites-beginning-monday-april-27/" rel="bookmark">Additional Lunch Sites Beginning Monday, April 27</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><time class="entry-date" datetime="2020-04-24T12:00:58-06:00">April 24, 2020</time>
</div>
<!-- .entry-meta -->
			
					</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
			<p>Dear Parents,</p>
<p>Starting on Monday, April 27 Lunch (with a to-go breakfast for the next day) will be served at four additional locations every day from 11 a.m. to noon. The new locations are listed below.</p>
<p>Breakfast and lunch are free to all children age 18 and younger<br>
Please maintain social distancing by staying in your vehicle for curbside service. If you are walking to the school, please stay at least six feet apart as you line up. Please do not come for a meal if you are sick.</p>
<p>The four NEW LOCATIONS for lunch and breakfast service together at 11 a.m. beginning April 27:</p>
<ul>
<li>Riverton Elementary</li>
<li>Ridge View Elementary</li>
<li>Midas Creek Elementary</li>
<li>Silvercrest Elementary</li>
</ul>
<p>The following sites will continue to offer lunch and breakfast service together at 11 a.m.:</p>
